Class StatementExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • fitnesse.slim.StatementExecutor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StatementExecutorInterface

    public class StatementExecutor
extends Object
implements StatementExecutorInterface
    This is the API for executing a SLIM statement. This class should not know about the syntax of a SLIM statement.
